nodes.text: Datafile Sub-J, also known as sourcefile 56211217.KXYR.170649, was part of the Suspected Activities Considered Against the Interests and/or Benefit of Alliance Operations and/or Security document maintained by the Alliance to Restore the Republic. The information contained in the datafile was edited and compiled to fill out the "Suspected and Potential Threat" section on SecuriDexs issued by the Task Force on Alliance Security.
